         <abstract>
            <p>Infinite integrals involving Bessel functions are recast, by means of an Abel transform, in terms of Fourier integrals. As there are many efficient numerical methods for computing Fourier integrals, this leads to a convenient way of approximating Bessel function integrals.</p>
          </abstract>
